  <span id="freeText1254198553130109725" style="display:none"><b>4 STARS</b><br><br><img src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/hostedimages/1448373334i/17131334._SY540_.jpg" class="gr-hostedUserImg"><br><br>And the <b>Will Trent</b> story goes on. <br><br><b>
  <i>
    <blockquote>There has to be something awfully bad or awfully good to compel a person to turn their lives around.</blockquote>
  </i>
