  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2835134712" />
    <a title="Laura Peden" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/75854317-laura-peden"><img alt="Laura Peden" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1623732580p2/75854317.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2835134712?book_show_action=true">Jun 17, 2019</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Laura Peden" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Laura Peden" href="/user/show/75854317-laura-peden">Laura Peden</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/75854317-laura-peden?shelf=audible">audible</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/75854317-laura-peden?shelf=audiobooks">audiobooks</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2835134712" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer12902973718062675713">Broken by Karin Slaughter is book 4 in The Will Trent series. This one is quite a bit different than the others in the series. I didn’t even have to take a break from reading because of torture scenes. It’s definitely more a of a mystery than a thriller, heavier on forensics than the others and there’s more character development to set up the future books. I enjoyed the slower pace of this one and I completely adore Sarah’s character so I was happy she was featured throughout. I really hope ther</span>
  <span id="freeText12902973718062675713" style="display:none">Broken by Karin Slaughter is book 4 in The Will Trent series. This one is quite a bit different than the others in the series. I didn’t even have to take a break from reading because of torture scenes. It’s definitely more a of a mystery than a thriller, heavier on forensics than the others and there’s more character development to set up the future books. I enjoyed the slower pace of this one and I completely adore Sarah’s character so I was happy she was featured throughout. I really hope there’s a future for her and Will eventually. On to the next! </span>
  <a data-text-id="12902973718062675713" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
